[0m[49m[39m  163, 186[0m:[39m[49m ### Ingredients
[0m[49m[39m  164, 187[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 165     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | AWS Service | Role |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 166     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m |------------|------|
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 167     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Amazon SageMaker** | Trains and hosts demand forecasting models for surgical volume prediction |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 168     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **AWS Lambda** | Orchestrates pipeline: assembles constraints, triggers solver, handles reallocation logic |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 169     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Amazon ECS (Fargate)** | Runs CPU-intensive MIP solver (HiGHS, CBC, or commercial solver in container) |
